== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
《分歧者3：赤誠者》獲得了多為負面的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]評級12%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_divergent_series_allegiant/ |title=The Divergent Series: Allegiant (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=March 17, 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117191709/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_divergent_series_allegiant |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分33<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-divergent-series-allegiant |title=The Divergent Series: Allegiant reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=March 17, 2016 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929005531/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-divergent-series-allegiant |dead-url=no }}</ref>；主要被專業影評人認為雖然本片比前作《叛亂者》好一些，但其故事份量仍不足（僅為原作小說《赤誠者》的一部分，剩下的部分計畫在續作《超越者》中演出），使得被拉長的該系列越來越使人厭倦。

=== 票房 ===
電影在法國、義大利、比利時、荷蘭和瑞典等45個國家搶先美國上映，其首映週末獲得2520萬美元的票房。美國首週票房收入為2905萬美元，為系列成績最低。

中国大陆累计1.21亿人民币。

== 續集 ==
該系列的最後一部電影，《分歧者4：超越者》（The Divergent Series: Ascendant）{{notetag|原本官方暫定名為《分歧者3：赤誠者 II》（The Divergent Series: Allegiant – Part 2）。}}宣布計畫將在2017年3月24日在美國推出<ref name="BSL"/>。後來改為2017年6月9日上映<ref name="move back">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/power-rangers-divergent-movie-shailene-woodley-1201664379/|title='Power Rangers,' Final 'Divergent' Movie's Release Dates Moved Back|last=McNary|first=Dave|author-link=Dave McNary|work=Variety|date=December 17, 2015|access-date=December 19, 2015|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222170954/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/power-rangers-divergent-movie-shailene-woodley-1201664379/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。史溫凱退出執導<ref>{{cite web |url= https://deadline.com/2016/02/robert-schwentke-divergent-ascendant-shailene-woodley-theo-james-1201698820/ |title= Robert Schwentke Exits 'Divergent' Finale 'Ascendant' |work= Deadline |date= 8 February 2016 |access-date= 1 March 2018 |author= Fleming, Mike |archive-date= 2021-02-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210226114346/https://deadline.com/2016/02/robert-schwentke-divergent-ascendant-shailene-woodley-theo-james-1201698820/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，導演改為{{link-en|李·托蘭德·克萊格|Lee Toland Krieger}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Ascendant Lands Age of Adaline's Lee Toland Krieger to Direct Divergent Finale|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/nws/661757-ascendant-lands-age-of-adalines-lee-toland-krieger-to-direct-divergent-finale#/slide/1|access-date=1 March 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.movieinsider.com/m12598/allegiant---part-2|title=The Divergent Series: Ascendant Movie (Pre-Production): Dec. 29, 2016 - added Lionsgate as a distributor|publisher=Movie Insider|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2018-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701055201/https://www.movieinsider.com/m12598/allegiant---part-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年7月，據報導，因《赤誠者》票房表現不佳，使得《分歧者4：超越者》改以電視電影發行，並推出衍生電視劇。伍德莉表示，如果改成電視劇她就辭演<ref>{{cite web|title=‘Divergent’ Finale to Skip Theaters, Launch as a TV Movie and Spinoff Series (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/divergent-series-ascendant-1201818694/|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217183943/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/divergent-series-ascendant-1201818694/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來她真的在2017年2月正式退出。電視電影胎死腹中後，2018年12月時[[Starz_(电视频道)|Starz]]也宣布，因為一眾主演和電視台高層對電視劇版不感興趣，他們不會再推動企劃<ref name=Buzzfeed>{{cite web|url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/kateaurthur/divergent-franchise-disaster|title=How "Divergent" Turned Into A Disaster|date=2018-12-18|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120234640/https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/kateaurthur/divergent-franchise-disaster|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tvseriesfinale.com">{{cite web|url=https://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/ascendant-starz-no-longer-developing-tv-show-to-wrap-up-divergent-movie-series/|title=Ascendant: Starz No Longer Developing TV Show to Wrap Up Divergent Movie Series|date=2018-12-21|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801214513/https://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/ascendant-starz-no-longer-developing-tv-show-to-wrap-up-divergent-movie-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

